ZH: 我昨天晚上突然腹泻了。
EN: I suddenly had diarrhea last night.

ZH: 他因为吃了变质的食物而出现腹泻。
EN: He got diarrhea from eating spoiled food.

ZH: 她腹泻了一整个晚上，感觉很难受。
EN: She had diarrhea all night and felt very uncomfortable.

ZH: 小孩子常常会因为胃肠不适而出现腹泻。
EN: Children often get diarrhea due to stomach discomfort.

ZH: 医生告诉我多喝水对治疗腹泻很有帮助。
EN: The doctor told me that drinking more water is helpful in treating diarrhea.

ZH: 吃药可以缓解腹泻的症状。
EN: Taking medication can alleviate the symptoms of diarrhea.

ZH: 饮食不规律会导致腹泻。
EN: Irregular eating habits can lead to diarrhea.

ZH: 腹泻可能是肠道疾病的症状之一。
EN: Diarrhea may be a symptom of intestinal diseases.

ZH: 食物中毒常常会引起剧烈的腹泻症状。
EN: Food poisoning often causes severe diarrhea symptoms.

ZH: 腹泻通常是身体排毒的一种方式。
EN: Diarrhea is usually a way for the body to detoxify.

ZH: 长期腹泻可能会导致身体脱水。
EN: Prolonged diarrhea may lead to dehydration.

ZH: 坚持饮食清淡可以减少腹泻的发生率。
EN: Eating a light diet regularly can reduce the occurrence of diarrhea.

ZH: 做运动有助于缓解腹泻的症状。
EN: Exercising can help alleviate the symptoms of diarrhea.

ZH: 注意个人卫生是预防腹泻的重要措施。
EN: Paying attention to personal hygiene is an important measure to prevent diarrhea.

ZH: 孕妇患上腹泻需要及时就医。
EN: Pregnant women with diarrhea need to seek medical attention promptly.

ZH: 孩子遭受腹泻的折磨，妈妈心疼不已。
EN: The child suffered from the torment of diarrhea, causing the mother to feel distressed.

ZH: 腹泻是许多感染性疾病的典型症状。
EN: Diarrhea is a typical symptom of many infectious diseases.

ZH: 避免进食不洁食物可以减少患腹泻的风险。
EN: Avoiding eating contaminated food can reduce the risk of getting diarrhea.

ZH: 老年人容易因为消化系统减弱而出现腹泻。
EN: Elderly people are prone to diarrhea due to a weakened digestive system.
